        FROM [FinOps] AS [a]
        WHERE (([a].[AccFromId] = @__orgAccountId_0) OR ([a].[AccToId] = @__orgAccountId_1)) AND ([a].[FinOpDate] >= @__lastBalanceFixing_BalanceDate_2))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END (6438bdd5)

        WHERE (([a].[AccFromId] = @__orgAccountId_0) OR ([a].[AccToId] = @__orgAccountId_1)) AND ([a].[FinOpDate] >= @__lastBalanceFixing_BalanceDate_2))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END (6438bdd5)

        FROM [FinOps] AS [a]
